      <title>以色列吹嘘袭击伊朗取得战略利益，但暗中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/israel-boasts-strategic-gains-from-attack-on-iran-but-quietly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在派遣 100 多架战斗机袭击伊朗后，以色列政府试图走一条微妙的路线：以色列官员认为这次袭击造成了重大战略破坏，但又希望伊朗继续认为不值得回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/israel-boasts-strategic-gains-from-attack-on-iran-but-quietly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 16:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安大略省省长表示，将延长汽油税减免至 2025 年 6 月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/ontario-to-extend-gas-tax-cut-through-june-2025-premier-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安大略省省长道格·福特在周日的新闻发布会上表示，安大略省计划将汽油和柴油税的临时减税措施延长至明年 6 月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/ontario-to-extend-gas-tax-cut-through-june-2025-premier-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 15:38:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场遭遇抛售，将迎来为期 10 天的考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/a-10-day-test-is-coming-for-bond-market-battered-by-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国债券市场已经遭遇了六个月来最严重的抛售，目前正进入关键的两周，这可能会决定今年剩余时间的走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/a-10-day-test-is-coming-for-bond-market-battered-by-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着盈利增长放缓，大型科技股失去部分光环</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/big-tech-stocks-lose-some-of-their-aura-as-earnings-growth-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利润增长放缓正在削弱股市科技巨头的坚不可摧性，因为它们正准备在本周公布业绩。它们能否扭转这一趋势将在很大程度上决定股市能否继续上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/big-tech-stocks-lose-some-of-their-aura-as-earnings-growth-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
